snippet.title: Tiger's Invasion (Telugu) | Tiger Nageswara Rao | Ravi Teja | Vamsee | Abhishek Agarwal Arts
snippet.description:
TIGER'S MENACING INVASION BEGINS 🐅
#TigerNageswaraRao 🥷 Teaser out now💥

In cinemas on October 20th 💥

#RaviTeja #Vamsee #AbhishekAgarwal #NupurSanon #GayatriBharadwaj #RenuDesai #MayankSinghaniya #AbhishekAgarwalArts

Mass Maharaja Ravi Teja and Vamsee’s Pan India Project #TigerNageswaraRao to be produced by Abhishek Agarwal under Abhishek Agarwal Arts and to be presented by Tej Narayan Agarwal.

Tiger Nageswara Rao will be made in Telugu, Hindi, Tamil, Kannada, and Malayalam languages. Based on the life of the notorious thief from Stuartpuram, Tiger Nageswara Rao is going to be highest budgeted film for Ravi Teja. This will mark first Pan India project of the actor.

GV Prakash Kumar will score muic for the film that has dialogues by Srikanth Vissa. R Madhie ISC will crank the camera and Avinash Kolla is the production designer. Mayank Singhaniya is the co-producer.

Cast: Ravi Teja, Nupur Sanon, Gayatri Bharadwaj and others
Writer, Director: Vamsee
Producer: Abhishek Agarwal
Banner: Abhishek Agarwal Arts
Presenter: Tej Narayan Agarwal
Co-Producer: Mayank Singhaniya
Dialogues: Srikanth Vissa
Music Director: GV Prakash Kumar
DOP: R Madhie
DI - B2H
Colorist - S. Raghunath varma
Production Designer: Avinash Kolla
PRO: Vamsi-Shekar
Marketing: FirstShow
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: Every Girls School On Independence Day | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
This video shows what happens in every girls school on Independence day. Scenarios like going on shopping with Indian mom to fancy dress shop , singing lessons for 15th august function in school , singing vande matram , choir selection of students , dance practices and coping up with syllabus , science teacher , other subject mam scolding and pissed off with students for missing their periods ,  dancing on desh rangila , dressing up for school function putting makeup , lots of red lipstick , rented jewellery , gudda , making bun , dressing up as different states punjab , gujrat , kashmir , west bangal , kolkata , assam , maharashtra , marathi , tamil , kanayakumari , chennia , school dance competition , making vlog in school , disscusing which class performed the best , hooting for our friends , class party on independence day bringing homemade food our cooks for us pao bhaji , cheese sandwiches , speaking on stage on democratic india , secular india , decorating class , cutting glaze paper , making chart paper on freedom fighters , rani laxmi baxi , jhansi ki rani , bhagat singh , gandhi ji , tricolor balloon decoration , making indian flag , indian mom arranging artificial jewellery for daughters school fancy dress , sewing her dress for proper fitting , maa vs beti , maa beti , our favs chinky and savitri , Patang baazi , Getting together on friend's terrace , beer bottles, Instagram photos with Indian flag , Girls doing Tricolour Eye makeup looks , School functions, 15 august dance practice in school, School life and choir singing on desh bhakhti songs , Fancy dress shopping for like Jhansi Ki Rani Mahatma Gandhi ji , Bhagat singh , freedom fighters , Getting laddoos , munch chocolate in School snacks , middle class family watching parade on Tv , forwarding Whatsapp messages of Swatantra Diwas going out for watching movie and so much more.. 
You will be filled with nostalgia for your school days .
Relive and Relish your School life.. These are the best days of school
Do share it with your friends , family , teachers , mothers , dost especially with school ones.. 
Happy Independence Day Everyone 🇮🇳
SCHOOL LIFE IS BEST. JAI HIND

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2│Flowers│EP# 316
snippet.description:
അഭിനയമോഹം തലയ്ക്ക് പിടിച്ചിരിക്കുകയാണ് രാം കുമാറിന്. ലച്ചുവും ദിയയും പലതുംപറഞ്ഞ് പിന്തിരിപ്പിക്കാൻ ശ്രമിക്കുന്നുണ്ടെങ്കിലും രാം കുമാർ രണ്ടും കൽപ്പിച്ചാണ്. ആരെയും വകവയ്ക്കാതെ അഭിനയമോഹവുമായി മുന്നോട്ട് പോകുന്ന രാം കുമാറിന് നിർദേശങ്ങളുമായി ബാലുവും ഒപ്പമുണ്ട്. ഇനി എന്തൊക്കെ സംഭവിക്കുമെന്ന് കാത്തിരുന്ന് കാണാം.

'Uppum Mulakum' is the favorite sitcom of Malayalees. The show, which travels through Balu, Neelu and their four children's lives. This show brings the humor, emotions and problems of a middle-class family's daily life to the audience in an interesting way. We will have to wait and see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'?

#UppumMulakum2 #BijiSopanam #NishaSarang #flowerstv

snippet.description:

Episode 3852: Long Drive Ke Sapne
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha phones Taarak and requests that he accompany him to his shop. Taarak accepts Jetha's invitation, and the two agree to meet in the Gokuldham society. While Jetha is waiting for his companion, Taarak Bhide approaches and offers to join them. Jetha becomes immersed in his fantasy of a lengthy drive with Babita, but Bhide interrupts his daydream. Babita later arrives in her car and offers Jetha a ride. Jetha is overjoyed and rushes inside the car. Jetha receives a call from Champaklal, and he cancels the trip with Babita.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3852, 17 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Sirf Tum Episode 35 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 17th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin

snippet.title: Ajay Devgn Threatens Murali Sharma | Singham | Movie Scene
snippet.description:
An honest and valiant policeman, Bajirao Singham, fights against injustice. However, when he encounters a corrupt politician, Jaikant Shikre, he deAn honest and valiant policeman, Bajirao Singham, fights against injustice. However, when he encounters a corrupt politician, Jaikant Shikre, he decides to teach him a lesson. #singham 

Bajirao Singham is a police sub- inspector who hails from a small town of Sawantwadi in Maharashtra. He fights against corruption with the valor of lion. 

When Kavya comes to Sawantwadi, from Goa to visit her grandparents on a vacation she is charmed by Bajirao's bold and courageous demeanor.

Everything goes well for Singham until there is a clash with a goon that eventually escalates into a full blown fight. Singham eventually gets promoted & is transferred to Goa which also happens to be the operational hub of the goon.

While this move brings Singham closer to Kavya, it also brings him in the clutches of the very same goon who is on a mission to destroy him. How Singham rises to the challenge to expose this crook and put an end to his malicious activities forms the rest of the story.

Starcast: Ajay Devgn, Kajal Aggarwal and Prakash Raj
Directed by: Rohit Shetty

snippet.title: What Happened When I Met Kamal Sir after Beast? Nelson Interview with Krishna
snippet.description:
Welcome to another episode of Deep Focus! In this special edition, we sit down with the acclaimed director, Nelson Dilipkumar. Dive into the behind-the-scenes journey of his recent blockbuster, "Jailer." Nelson sheds light on his unique writing process, the art of character creation, and the inspiration behind his storytelling. Don't miss out on this insightful conversation, where cinema meets the mind of its creator. Subscribe and stay tuned for more deep dives into the world of film. 🎬✨

We asked the Indian Film Industry for their Top 5 Favourite Films of All Time. Here's what they told us: https://www.filmcompanion.in/best-indian-films-forever/2023

What's your favourite film of all time? Vote NOW & be a part of the BIFF People's Edition List! : https://www.filmcompanion.in/best-indian-films-forever/2023/results

Visit us at http://filmcompanion.in

Do Like, Share, Comment & Subscribe to our channel.
Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/c/FilmCompanionSouth

Follow Us On:
https://www.facebook.com/FCompanionSouth
https://twitter.com/fcompanionsouth
https://instagram.com/filmcompanionsouth

Follow Us On:
https://www.facebook.com/filmcompanion
https://www.twitter.com/filmcompanion
http://instagram.com/filmcompanion

About Film Companion South:
Film Companion South is a division of Film Companion, founded by film critic and author Anupama Chopra. Apart from film reviews and articles, Film Companion South, with programs in Tamil, Malayalam, Telugu, and Kannada, specializes in conducting in-depth interviews with film personalities which include the likes of Kamal Hassan, Mani Ratnam, Academy Award-winner AR Rahman, Vetrimaaran, Dhanush, Yash, Sruthi Hariharan, Mahesh Babu, NTR Jr, Samantha, Aishwarya Rajesh, Ramya Krishnan, Prithviraj, Anjali Menon, Mysskin, Gautam Vasudev Menon, Rajamouli, Ram Charan, Yash, Prashanth Neel, Venkat Prabhu, Nelson, Sivakarthikeyan, Rakshit Shetty and many more. The channel has also hosted shows which open up the lesser-known facets of filmmaking with conversations with PC Sreeram, Ravi Varman, Rajiv Menon, Thota Tharani, and Academy Award-winner Resul Pookutty. In other words, Film Companion South is for those who love their cinema and are unapologetic about it.

snippet.title: Easily 3 Star Clashiversary Challenge #3 (Clash of Clans)
snippet.description:
The Clash of Clans 2023 Clashiversary Event progresses to Challenge 3. The Future Queen Skin is showcased in this level designed by Yuta14. It involves a Queen Charge strategy to the Town Hall and can be tricky if you have not done it before. I did want to thank iTzu for helping me with the consistency of this method - namely how to save all of the troops until after the TH is destroyed. If you activate it too early it can end up taking down your healers. Best of luck with your 3 stars!

Episode 29: A Breach Of Trust
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Reyansh confronts Revati when he finds out that Aradhna was telling the truth. Meanwhile, Aradhna arrives at her mother's house with the bakery order. Will Reyansh be able to find out Aradhna and apologise. Will Aradhna be able to know the truth about her mom? Stay tuned to find out what turn Reyansh and Aradhna's life takes.

Show Name: Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka
Cast: Shivangi Joshi, Kushal Tandon
Episode: 29
Director: Atif Khan
Producer: Ekta Kapoor

#barsateinmausampyaarka #setindia #बरसातेंमौसमप्यारका #kushaltandon #shivangijoshi 


About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. While united in their passion for honest and ground-breaking journalism, their contrasting characters immediately puts them at loggerheads. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐄𝐍𝐓𝐒:

Ingredients For Peanut Barfi -
* Roasted Peanuts (भुनी हुई मूँगफली) - 250 Gm
* Sugar (चीनी) - 200 Gm
* Water (पानी) - 75 Ml
* Milk Powder (दूध का पाउडर) - 3 Tbsp
* Ghee (घी) - 1 Tbsp
* Almond (बादाम) - 8-10
* Cashew Nut (काजू) - 8-10
* Pistachio (पिस्ता) - 8-10
* Soaked Saffron Water (भिगोया हुआ केसर पानी) - 1 Tbsp
* Butter Paper (बटर पेपर) - As Required


𝐑𝐄𝐂𝐈𝐏𝐄:
Take a tray or any tin, keep the butter paper in it, grease some Ghee, and keep it aside.
Roast the Peanuts on low heat and stir from time to time until they become crunchy. Then take them out on a plate & let them cool down. Then rub them between your palms & peel them off easily. Put them in a mixing jar & coarsely grind and make the Peanut Powder, then sieve the Peanut Powder. Put some Milk Powder & mix well. In a pan, put some Water and Sugar and make 1 string of Sugar Syrup. Then put the Peanut Powder in the Syrup gradually. Stir it continuously & make it lumps-free & thick. Then put some Ghee in it, and mix it well. At last, transfer the mixture to a greased tray & spread well. Dry roast some Almonds, Cashews & Pistachios for 2-4 minutes on a slow flame. 
In the same pan, put Sugar & cook it on medium flame till it melts. When Sugar gets melted, put roasted Dry Fruits & mix them well. At last, put Saffron Water & cook for a  while. Then immediately after put the caramelized mixture on the Peanut mixture & spread well. Keep it set overnight at room temperature. Then take it out on a plate and cut it into pieces & enjoy! In this way, super soft and tasty Peanut Chikki/Mithai/ Barfi will get ready at home.

-------------------------------------

snippet.title: Sirf Tum Episode 36 Teaser - 17th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Episode 36 Teaser - 17th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast: 
Anmol Baloch - Abeer
Hamza Sohail - Hannan
Mohsin Abbas - Hamza
Sakina Khan - Amal
Fazila Kazi - Farah

Erum Akhter - Mahrukh
Ayesha Gul - Amina

Salma Asim - Noreen

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3851 | 16 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3851: Saare Bhartiya Bhai Bhai
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide notifies Champaklal that Tapu Sena has now consented to make preparations for the Gokuldham Society's Independence Day event. Champaklal counsels Bhide on how to cope with the new generation of children, and Bhide decides to follow Champaklal's advice. Babita and Iyer are surprised to discover the spectacular decor at Gokuldham the next morning, and they admire Tapu Sena's work. Everyone celebrates Tapu Sena's piece of art, yet it quickly vanishes. Bhide becomes enraged once more and decides to begin the flag-raising ceremony without them. So, where has Tapu Sena gone?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3851, 16 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

ഹൃദയം നുറുങ്ങുന്ന വേദനയിലാണ് പ്രതീഷ്. എന്നാൽ സുരഭിക്കും സുഹാസിനിക്കും ഇടയിലുള്ള മഞ്ഞുരുകുന്നില്ല. സുഹാസിനിയുടെ മനസ്സിൽ സുരഭിയോടുള്ള വെറുപ്പിന്റെ കാർമേഘങ്ങൾ മൂടുകയാണ്. സുരഭിയോടുള്ള അമർഷം സുഹാസിനി പലവിധത്തിലാണ് പ്രകടിപ്പിക്കുന്നത്. എന്താണ് സുഹാസിനിക്ക് ഇത്ര ദേഷ്യം എന്നറിയാനുള്ള ആകാംക്ഷയിലാണ് കുടുംബാംഗങ്ങൾ. ഇനി എന്തൊക്കെയാണ് സുരഭിക്ക് നേരിടേണ്ടി വരുക?

Pratish is in heart wrenching pain. Suhasini expresses her anger towards Surabhi in various ways. The family members are eager to know what made Suhasini so angry. What will Surabhi have to face now?

#SurabhiyumSuhasiniyum #MallikaSukumaran

snippet.title: Meet Shark Anupam Mittal | Sandeep Maheshwari | Hindi
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

snippet.title: 1 कप पोहा से 10 मिनट में बनाए खस्ता कुरकुरा नाश्ता जो पूरे 2 महीने तक खाए /Masala papdi
snippet.description:
Siri Rs 20 /- mein tayyar karein 1/2 kg Masala Papdi…1 Cup Pohe se Sirf 10 minute mein ban jata hai…aur pure 2 marine ise kha saktein …ekdum kasta kurkura nashta hai…jisse aap sham ke shamay garma-garm Chai ke sath khaye …Khasta Nashta…Store upto 2 months …Tea time Snacks…Masala Papdi

Ingredients
1. Flattened Rice  1 Cup
2. Gram Flour 1/2 Cup
3. Water 1 tbsp
4. Refined Oil 1 tsp
5. Cumin Seeds 1/2 tsp
6. Asafoetida 1/4 tsp
7. Turmeric Powder 1/4 tsp
8. Red Chilli Flakes 1 tsp
9. Black Sesame Seeds 1 tsp
10. Coriander Leaves 1/4 Cup
11. Garam Masala 1/4 tsp
12. Dry Mango Powder 1/2 tsp
13. Salt as per taste

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 31 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 15th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

-------------------------------------------------
After Kaashvi has body tremors and becomes unconscious, Baalveer and Benaam attempt to restore her health. Baalveer attempts to seek assistance from his mother, Adishi, who comes from another realm. She informs Baalveer about the black hole, which has the ability to pull any powerful magic from anything. Benaam informs Baalveer that the black hole is so powerful that it could collide with the sun. Benaam tries to hide herself when Maha Mahim Uttan pays a visit to Baalveer. We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: ये देश है वीर जवानों का | Independence Day Special Desh Bhakti Song 2023 | Best Desh Bhakti Geet
snippet.description:
ये देश है वीर जवानों का अलबेलों का मस्तानों का | Independence Day Special 2023 | Desh Bhakti Geet 
------
Song: Yeh Desh Hai Veer Jawanon Ka
Movie: Naya Daur
Singer: Mohammed Rafi, Balbir
Music Director: O.P. Nayyar
Film Star: Dilip Kumar, Vyjayanthimala, Ajeet, Chand Usmani, Nazir Hussain, Leela Chitnis, Johnny Walker
Director: B.R. Chopra,
Lyricist: Sahir Ludhianvi
------
Lyrics:
o ye desh hai veer jawano ka
albelo ka mastano ka
is desh ka yaaro hoy
is desh ka yaaro kya kahna
ye desh hai duniya ka gahna

o yaha chaudi chaati veero ki
yaha bholi shakle heero ki
yaha gaate hai raanjhe hoy
yaha gaate hai raanjhe masti me
masti hai jhume basti me

o pedo pe bahare jhulo ki
raaho me kataare phulo ki
yaha hasta hai saawan hoy
yaha hasta hai saawan baalo me
khilti hai kaliya gaalo me

o kahi dangal surkh jawano ke
kahi kartab teer kamano ke
yaha nit nit mele hoy
yaha nit nit mele sajte hai
nit dhol aur tashe bajte hai

o dilbar ke liye dildaar hai ham
dushman ke liye talwar hai ham
maindaan me agar ham
maindaan me agar ham dat jaaye
